        {
          "key": "hatchery_status",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Christian",
            "text": "The hatchery is temporarily closed for system upgrades.\n\nWe're recalibrating water filtration and breeding protocols.\n\nUntil then, focus on sustainable wild fishing with Vincent.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "Do you have any advice about fishing?",
                "resultDialogId": "fishing_advice",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Thanks for the information.",
                "resultDialogId": "end_conversation",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "fishing_advice",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Christian",
            "text": "From a scientific perspective: monitor the Population Health Meter closely.\n\nIt's a direct indicator of ecosystem stress. Below 40% requires immediate action.\n\nRemember, sustainable fishing isn't just practice—it's data-driven responsibility.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "What about processing fish?",
                "resultDialogId": "processing_advice",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Thanks for the advice.",
                "resultDialogId": "end_conversation",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "processing_advice",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Christian",
            "text": "Processing efficiency is measurable. Clean cuts reduce waste by approximately 15%.\n\nRuben can teach you proper technique. Waste reduction equals sustainability increase.\n\nIt's a simple equation with significant environmental impact.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "What about the hatchery's future?",
                "resultDialogId": "hatchery_future",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Thanks for the advice.",
                "resultDialogId": "end_conversation",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "hatchery_future",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Christian",
            "text": "The hatchery will reopen once system integrity is verified.\n\nWe plan to reintroduce sustainable breeding programs for local species.\n\nBut for now, your focus should be on mastering wild fishing stewardship.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "Thanks for the information.",
                "resultDialogId": "end_conversation",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "hello_response",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Christian",
            "text": "Acknowledged. Hello.\n\nIf you require stewardship advice, I recommend consulting Vincent or Ruben.\n\nThe hatchery will resume operations at a future date.",
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "end_conversation",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Christian",
            "text": "Conversation terminated. Return to your stewardship duties.\n\nRemember: sustainable practices are quantifiable. Measure your impact.",
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "post_fishing_tutorial",
          "value": {
